window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Jason has uncovered three dragon misfits. Now he must find the rest before Therin gains controls of them. </b></p> <p>Now that his sister knows of the dragons, Jason doesn't feel as isolated in their small village. The connection to the dragons lets him protect his people along with the existence of the dragons. </p> <p>An attack on his home village forces Jason to go to Lachen and stop Therin for good. To do so, he'll need the help of all the dragon misfits, but can the forest dragon help him master the art of illusion in time for him to save his people?</p>"; 
